Drop MP3 / M4A / FLAC / OGG files here, then run:

    docker compose --profile tools run --rm importer

Or point the importer at any folder:

    IMPORT_DIR=/path/to/your/music docker compose --profile tools run --rm importer

Sub-folders are scanned recursively. Same-stem .lrc lyrics and .jpg/.png
artwork files are picked up automatically; embedded ID3 artwork is also
extracted when no sidecar image is present.
